name: 0XLSD
description: 0xLSD is a decentralized liquidity provision protocol that supports multi-chain aggregation. 0xLSD is built on the Binance Smart Chain (#BSC), Arbitrum (#ARB) and Ethereum (#ETH) public chains, with the aim of creating stable and sustainable liquidity for the Web3 world, while also constructing a comprehensive financial service system on top of it.
